Louis XIV kɛ Fɩɖansɩ tʊ. Palʊlɩ-ɩ Fɩɖansɩ ɛjaɖɛ taa kɛ ɛjaɖɛ kewiyaɣ ɖaɣ nakʊ ñɩŋgaɣ taa kɛ Saint-Germain-en-Laye kɛ evemiye kagbanzɩ ŋgʊ wiye salaŋ fenaɣ taa kɛ pɩnaɣ 1638. Nɛ ɛsɩ kɔɔnɔɔ evemiye wiye salaŋ fenaɣ taa kɛ pɩnaɣ 1715 kɛ Versailles kɛ fɩɖansɩ peɖe. Ɛɛ-kɛ fɩɖansɩ nɛ Navaɖɖɛ pɛdɛ wiyau susɔ. Pɩgbaʊ nɛ evemiye hiu nɛ naanaza agoza fenaɣ taa pɩnaɣ 1643 yɔ, Louis XIV ka-kɛnaɣ Fɩɖansɩ nɛ Navaɖɖɛ paa-ɛjɛɛ kewiyaɣ ɖiuu pɩkɔ pɩtalɩ ɛsɩm wiye kɛ kɔɔnɔɔ evemiye wiye salaŋ fenaɣ taa kɛ pɩnaɣ 1715. Ɛ-caa kɛ payaɣ se Louis XIII nɛ ɛ-ɖoo kɛlɛ Anne d'Autriche. Ɛwɛnaɣ halaa naalɛ nɛ piya loɖo. Ɛ-caa sɩm wayɩ lɛ, ɛ-pɩɣa Né Louis wey i ɛtasaɣ sɛʊ hɩɖɛ se Dieudonné, kʊɖʊm ɛnʊ lɛ Louis XIV, kpaɣ kewiyaɣ kpelaɣ. Fenasɩ pasɩ wayi lɛ, pɩcɔ ɛlakaɣ ɛtɛ pɩnzɩ kagbanzɩ yɔɔ tɔsʊʊ lɛ, ɛ-kakɛ pɩnzɩ hiŋ loɖo nɛ naanaza tʊ tʊ kɛʊ wiyau kɛ Fɩɖansɩ ɛjaɖɛ kewiyaɣ kpelaɣ yɔ, nɛ hiŋ naanaza nɛ naanaza wiyau kɛ Navaɖɖɛ ɛjaɖɛ taa. Ɛkɛ ɖɔɖɔ wiyau naadozo tʊ kɛ Bourbons waɣ hɔlʊ taa kɛ Fɩɖansɩ ɛjaɖɛ taa. Louis XIV caɣ kewitu pɩnzɩ hiŋ lʊbɛ nɛ naalɛ nɛ fenasɩ naadozo nɛ avema hiu nɛ lutozo. Ɛ-kewitu tʊ Fɩɖansɩ ɛjaɖɛ taa, kɛ pɩyʊ kem kɛ ɖeɖe tɔm hɔlʊ taa kɛ anasaayɩwaa tɛ.

